metadata.name: Arosha
metadata.description:
Arosha is the daughter of the sun and the wind. 
She lives in the mountains of Ameretat and like a wild Spirit, she flies freely over the highest peaks.
She is the bravest guardian of her homeland and protects it from above.
Her white heart shines through her eyes. If you stare at her long enough, you'll discover her holy spirit behind her dazzling and magical looks.



This is a hand-painted watercolor painting on arches-rough paper.
Scanned in high resolution.

5635 x 8000
